'''好撒瑪利亞人醫院'''是一所位於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[聖荷西|聖荷西]]的[[醫院|醫院]]，自1996年起由[[美國醫院集團|美國醫院集團]]擁有<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1995-12-28/business/fi-18624_1_charity-care|title=Hospital Giant's Plans Spark Concern About Charity Care|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-date=2014-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031033646/http://articles.latimes.com/1995-12-28/business/fi-18624_1_charity-care|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==榮譽==
好撒瑪利亞人醫院是美國首五所主要中風中心（Primary Stroke Center）之一<ref name="today">{{cite web|url=http://goodsamsanjose.com/patients/our-hospital-today.dot|title=Our Hospital Today - Good Samaritan Hospital|accessdate=2013-05-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528082448/http://goodsamsanjose.com/patients/our-hospital-today.dot|archivedate=2013-05-28}}</ref>。

